reviewText: Another example of classic Danish erotica from the same folks who brought us the "In the Sign of..." series (each film devoted... ostensibly... to a sign of the zodiac).  Not recommended if you take offense to seeing people who lack some or all of their clothes.  This is quite different, however, from typical American "porno" which, if you like that sort of thing, is probably what you will prefer to this film.

I already gave five stars to all other flicks for this bunch of 6 or 7 and this is not really porno and not really anything and it doesnt pretend to be anything but chicks are nice, undress often and do what we expect them to do. And men are men--they chase tail, drink and worry about nothing.
A movie is a fiction so why pretend you know something other people dont? Why? Tell me. I watch something everyday but I learn fron real life experiencies not movies or TV or media.

It was ok, but if you have seen Ole Soltoft other films, it is right in line with them with less sex and more comedy.  Personally I prefer seeing the sex for the ladies are very beautiful and there are plots to this film.  I would like to see more climaxes as well.

A bit hardcore but with the fun feel of a softcore feature.  The story was interesting enough that I found myself actually reading the English subtitles.  Rather unusual, I thought, for this type of film.
